003,0,Gas Discharge Lamp
003,1,Current,Discharge Lamp,Range: 0.0...100.0 W\nSpecification: 32.0...65.0 W
003,2,Voltage,Discharge Lamp,Range: 0.0...100.0 V\nSpecification: 45.0...95.0 V
